responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "B9C573F9429AA4B55A713BA019D79FD8", "T\'kano lives to the northwest, on an island in the southwest of Rosewater Fen. His ways are slow, and few are allowed to see him. Patience and respect are required. He values sincerity above all; haste or lies will turn him away. If your heart is true and purpose pure, he will guide you. But you must listen not just to him, but to the spirits that speak through him.")
name: DD_0110_EotGH_Wiyakoni_29_Response
